opt65 version history

Version 1.1 - minor fixes, 2026 April 14

- fix the off-by-one in the line numbers in errors and warnings
- warnings no longer get reported more than once
- added warnings for non-ASCII characters that normally implies OCR issues
- added CI build machinery to automatically make binary downloads
- add homebrew and tap support

Version 1.0 - initial release, 2026

- basic functionality to parse 6502 code and produce binary and statistics
- command line switches WILL change in future versions!
